{"tid":913082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這張圖片太有魔性　讓你一整天頭暈目眩","createTime":"2018-11-23T06:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T08:37:12.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5e6708f5efadcbf5b1bf76258c5b4763621810","tid":913082,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdcE03P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdcE03P.png&h=8b571bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日國外網路流傳一張圖片，由簡單的幾何圖所拼成，但仔細盯著這張圖，卻會讓你一整天頭暈目眩。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這張圖由蜂巢格紋、紫色、黃色和紅色所組成，雖然圖片是靜態的，但在視覺的錯覺之下，讓人誤以為這是一張動態圖片。許多網友都回報，仔細盯著圖看，會讓人頭暈目眩。而網傳這張圖由日本一名心理學教授「山本羽島」(YamamotoHashima)所繪製，還稱觀眾對於這張圖的感受，就能反映出一個人的壓力程度。如果看著這張圖，覺得是靜止不動或動得很緩慢，就代表你的壓力不大；如果看起來動得快速且持續轉動，就代表你的壓力很大。<br />\n <br />\n但Instagram上一名網友「yuryfrom」就表示，他才是這張圖的原創人，是他在2016年9月的作品。他強調絕對不是「山本羽島」所繪製的，而且這個人也根本不存在。「yuryfrom」說，他是受到日本立命館大學心理學教授北岡明佳的「錯視圖」影響，才創作出這張圖片。"},{"pid":"e6cf64332b343e5afc24fefe23be081d9d888054","tid":913082,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"呢張一啲都唔smooth"},{"pid":"f17cc6eb6366e0d4568d526468c05dd6202a7de9","tid":913082,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"睇到笑左咁即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4516790cf1dcacf4e2981560ea51528b7415a7","tid":913082,"uid":3028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:36:47.000Z","msg":"屌 gif黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b447fca381788bd6d143516cc6343153e570ad09","tid":913082,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f17cc6eb6366e0d4568d526468c05dd6202a7de9","tid":913082,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"睇到笑左咁即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:37:16.000Z","msg":"即係你高強過佢"},{"pid":"511ca3bc96ef0d45072ae0023885a3793aed84de","tid":913082,"uid":22692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"個心好壓迫 頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb64f61c89798b54acbfb3b6ae6a3d168516a123","tid":913082,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33ca105e1d179d2c307166b3eef48adf97d5952f","tid":913082,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有郁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c962c6f69f7d293fac709f887c144d9ede9222","tid":913082,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"望實一個位就唔會有郁既錯覺"},{"pid":"7681ec03a337fe42372242476feda039998b2106","tid":913082,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54c962c6f69f7d293fac709f887c144d9ede9222","tid":913082,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"望實一個位就唔會有郁既錯覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:25:10.000Z","msg":"我調翻轉，望住個波會轉，望其他位唔轉"},{"pid":"80ee8bd06d5f0053d0b8d3bb575f8cadd33c60fc","tid":913082,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54c962c6f69f7d293fac709f887c144d9ede9222","tid":913082,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"望實一個位就唔會有郁既錯覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"我左望右望都唔覺佢郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{